7. x3_ddot + (L/2)sin(őł3)(őł3_dot)^2 - (L/2)cos(őł3)őł3_ddot - x2_ddot = 0  
8. y3_ddot - (L/2)cos(őł3)(őł3_dot)^2 - (L/2)sin(őł3)őł3_ddot - y2_ddot = 0  
9. őł3_ddot = 0

Because the bar rotates at constant angular speed,

őł3_dot = ŌČ  
őł3_ddot = 0

so the equations reduce to:

1. x1_ddot + y1_ddot = 0  
2. őł1_ddot = 0  
3. y2_ddot - x2_ddot = 0  
4. őł2_ddot = 0  
